        <mxCell id="flow-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#fff8e6;strokeColor=#d97706;fontFamily=JetBrains Mono,monospace;fontSize=10;fontColor=#1a1d27;arcSize=8;align=left;spacingLeft=10;html=1;verticalAlign=top;" value="&lt;b&gt;Runtime flow (setNews):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Client calls setNews() on NewsObservableImpl&lt;br/&gt;2. setNews() stores news, calls notifyObservers()&lt;br/&gt;3. Loop: each Observer.update(news) is called&lt;br/&gt;4. remove(channel1) → unsubscribed&lt;br/&gt;5. Next setNews() only notifies channel2" vertex="1">
